Moore
v.
Caldwell 158P16-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 9, 2016

Mr. Larry Brandon Moore, Pro Se

Mr. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, For Caldwell, Jesse B. (III) (Judge)

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 2nd of May 2016 by Petitioner for Petition for Order to Show Cause Under Common Law:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."
